		<p>Choice Hotels approached Taos Creative to create a microsite to host their online competitions. Separate competitions were held in Australia and New Zealand, so the requirements were to create a template where elements could be easily updated. The competitions were exclusive to Choice Hotels customers, therefore the client needed a secure gateway for users to log in.</p>

