		<h2>Solution</h2>
		<p>We designed a process where users can enter their unique ID which will grant access and automatically fill in the competition form. To entice users to subscribe to the company's Facebook page, we added a facebook plugin so entrants could "like" the page and receive additional rewards. The prompt loads on form completion, giving the user a choice to subscribe to the Facebook fan page.</p>
		<p>Wireframes and userflows were originally built using protoshare, a cloud based wireframing tool.</p>
